    "title": "Hiring Store Manager at The Coffee Bean India South Asia Partners",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Store Manager with drive and ambition, The Coffee Bean India South Asia Partners in Visakhapatnam is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout The Coffee Bean India South Asia Partners:\nThe Coffee Bean India South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Category Management\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with The Coffee Bean India South Asia Partners!",
